Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:10.78,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.01,0:00:19.29,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:31.59,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:37.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami was visiting the \NGolden Dawn's headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.48,0:00:39.76,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,in order to meet with Vangeance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,How long is that golden \Nweird mask guy captain of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:46.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,going to make me wait after he \Nsaid he wanted to apologize?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.24,0:00:48.77,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-He should be here any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:51.36,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Golden Dawn jerks messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.55,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami continued to wait for Vangeance,\Nwhom he trusted
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.57,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,because they had fought for this kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.57,0:01:00.58,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and become Magic Knights \NSquad captains together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.05,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:08.97,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance revealed his other self, which \Nhe had kept hidden, to the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:15.74,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was the Captain of the Golden Dawn,\N William Vangeance,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.64,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,but also the leader of the \NEye of the Midnight Sun, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:24.68,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, William... \NMy one and only human friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:29.44,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Good day to you, \NWizard King Julius Novachrono.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.07,0:01:34.44,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I am the leader of the \NEye of the Midnight Sun, Licht.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:39.03,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I had really hoped that wasn't the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:42.89,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Licht fought Julius so he \Ncould steal the magic stones
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.12,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,that Julius had and exact his \Nrevenge against the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Julius was able to anticipate Licht's attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,with his time magic and fight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.54,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I have you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:53.56,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Whaâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.21,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's anticipating even faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.61,0:01:59.84,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I can already see your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.57,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:36.09,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Julius Novachrono
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.83,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.95,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The castle tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.14,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something's shining...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.77,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.58,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.45,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.94,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,This magic... It's Lord Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.05,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,He's battling with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:11.95,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who uses light magic and \Ncan keep up with Lord Julius...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:13.02,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:15.52,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of \Nthe Midnight Sun, Licht?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:23.02,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,But the Royal Knights should be working \Non eliminating them as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.00,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,How did he get into the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:31.95,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Was he also the one who shut down my \Ncommunication magic with Lord Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.68,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many unknowns...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.82,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.35,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is Lord Julius fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.14,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.59,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Please, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.95,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,This is the moment our strength \Nwill be put to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:01.12,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot protect this kingdom \Nif we're panicking like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:03.92,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.24,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job to remain \Ncalm at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.81,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we were to assist in the fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:12.40,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,we're nowhere near their level. \NWe'd only get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.96,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Lord Julius should lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:19.79,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,but if all else fails, the only ones \Nwho could keep up in this battle are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.68,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights Squad captains or their equals!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.38,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I need to send a message to all the \NMagic Knights Squad headquarters I've marked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.30,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.92,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.43,main,Char,0000,0000,0000,,Communication magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.96,main,Bah,0000,0000,0000,,It's a message from the royal capital, bah-ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.31,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,This is an urgent message to all \NMagic Knights Squad captains!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.96,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,The Wizard King is fighting a \Nman believed to be the leader
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:43.63,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,of the Eye of the Midnight Sun \Nright now at Clover Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:48.24,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,They might be putting \Nsome plan into motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.95,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,like the previous attack \Non the royal capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.87,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,All Magic Knights should follow orders from\N their captains and guard their districts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:57.43,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Captains, as soon as your \Ndistricts are secure,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:05:59.35,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,please meet at the royal \Ncapital immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.20,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:06.14,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Mereoleona should be attacking \Ntheir hideout as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:09.89,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the Eye of the Midnight \NSun is at the royal capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:13.28,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,This could be my only chance\Nto avenge my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.28,italics,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:18.30,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those pathetic \Nlooks on your faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:21.48,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourselves members \Nof the proud Crimson Lion Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:22.28,main,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.17,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the words of my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:25.69,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,Remain calm at all times!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.69,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,While my sister is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:29.23,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,we will prepare for a possible attack
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.23,0:06:32.03,main,Leo,0000,0000,0000,,by the Eye of the Midnight Sun,\N as we were ordered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:34.75,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.54,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.94,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Crimson Lion Kings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:43.85,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened? \NHow did they get into the royal capital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.11,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry and return, \NCaptain Vangeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.68,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.47,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.93,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Your individual blows \Nare becoming a bit dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:18.70,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I won't even have to \Nanticipate your moves to dodge them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.52,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He can keep up with \Nme even at this speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:25.45,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far into the future \Ncan he anticipate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:35.82,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You can have this back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.74,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He sped up my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:50.64,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you certainly came close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.38,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Even reading your moves, I still \Nhaven't been able to capture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:09:00.28,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,What is behind this man's strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:03.83,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He's just an ordinary human. So why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:07.52,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really appreciate it \Nif you'd just give up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:11.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not wound Vangeance's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:15.61,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The reason he isn't fighting back is\Nbecause he wants to capture me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.38,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He still has plenty of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:20.38,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,To fight against me,\Ndespite my four-leaf grimoire...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:24.84,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it? Where is his grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.67,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.10,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Are you curious about my grimoire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:34.17,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,My grimoire is right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.22,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:41.49,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't even have a cover!\N That grimoire is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:45.42,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Time magic and a grimoire \Nwithout a cover...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:49.65,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know if it was good or bad \Nat the time, but I was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:52.70,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:56.59,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like this coverless grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:00.02,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:03.45,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I? What is my purpose in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.66,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I kept asking myself that over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.66,0:10:11.21,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And as I did, I gained \Nmore and more recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:14.71,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And once I finally got here, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:19.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The path that I've walked \Nmakes me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:25.56,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.69,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I just figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.23,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,We are about to use the \Npower of the magic stones
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.82,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,in an attempt to defy the \Nnatural order of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.16,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.23,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This human...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:47.34,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,He is an existence that the world and \Nfate created in order to stop us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.06,0:10:50.67,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The last bastion of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.30,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,As the Wizard King,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:55.42,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect this kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:58.67,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.11,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Then I suppose... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.22,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly why I have to defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:11.73,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,In that case... just try to protect them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:15.93,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Magic Released!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.22,0:11:20.82,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,His power is swelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.33,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.65,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.25,main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:39.42,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This tremendous magic power is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:52.44,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You humans stole everything from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:58.37,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,My friends... my days of \Nhappiness... all in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:01.45,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means violating the natural order...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:04.85,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,You humans shall pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:19.34,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,To think he had enough magic power \Nto overwhelm this entire kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:22.97,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. Is he planning to \Nunleash that power upon the people?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:26.14,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't kill you alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.39,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I can kill everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.76,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this a spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:34.10,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Countless swords of light?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:37.10,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, the sky's all white!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.40,main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,It's so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.98,0:12:41.61,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this the end of the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.50,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.03,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Town in the Common Realm: Nean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.03,top,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's so empyreal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.49,sign_12339_133_Finnes_Calmreich,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}A Village Out in the Boonies: Hage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:49.49,top,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.23,main,Nash,0000,0000,0000,,We can see it from way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.37,main,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:13:01.09,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Even if that \Nlight is something ominous,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:05.17,main,Lily,0000,0000,0000,,this kingdom has Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:13.35,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The size of that light spell \Nis ridiculous... damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.60,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on, Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.61,italics,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.98,0:13:26.78,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It's already enveloped the \Nwhole kingdom. At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:32.29,italics,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Now... Accept your judgment, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:36.55,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Light Magic: Arrows of Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.37,0:13:48.31,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I had doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:54.75,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, why do those commoners \Nhave such poor magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.51,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly don't know how \Npeasants are even alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:01.14,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick just being \Nin the same kingdom as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.78,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.70,flashbackitalics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.41,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.12,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.12,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Despite having high levels of magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:19.36,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,they only used it to line their own \Npockets and weren't of any use to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.13,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Why were they even alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.22,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you must be the Magic \NKnight I heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.62,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the bizarre grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:30.36,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that aside, there's a merchant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:34.19,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,who has requested our \Naccommodation of his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.13,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.13,0:14:36.46,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.83,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:46.99,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I kept searching for my purpose in life \Nwhile fighting as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:48.90,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:57.20,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and give me all your money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.21,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.24,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,You evil villain who threatens \Nthe peace in this kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.96,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:07.90,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I encountered a man named Zara,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:11.80,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,who was the first peasant to \Nbe chosen as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.15,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:17.97,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, my magic is a hundred \Ntimes stronger than yours, you fat-ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.64,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Knight, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:23.63,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Like that scares me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.73,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.37,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:41.50,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, get someplace safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:49.39,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Heya! Could you come down here a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.97,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't have much magic power,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.57,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,but he cleverly used his trap spells in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:59.52,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Observation of his magic made \Nit clear how hard he worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.56,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what the heck is that magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.45,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like you're \Nreversing the flow of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.82,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Close, but not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:12.94,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Time magic, eh? That's way too awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.07,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd say there won't be any casualties now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:20.93,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Zara, was it? Looks like \Nyou're quite hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:21.74,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:22.83,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.73,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,As a Magic Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.30,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,we need to prioritize the lives \Nof the people, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:29.71,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel the same way, Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:32.78,flashback,Zara,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll leave this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.78,0:16:35.84,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,While other Magic Knights were blinded \Nby personal achievements and glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:41.10,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,he always prioritized helping out \Nthe people above everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:45.38,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, even though I didn't really \Nknow what it meant to be a Magic Knight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:48.30,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was what a true \NMagic Knight should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.36,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,A little while later...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:53.11,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Zara had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.35,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:02.87,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.37,flashback,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:23.41,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Zara had carried out his \Nduty as a Magic Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.82,0:17:28.02,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I wanted to be... \Na Magic Knight like Zara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.02,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,And right around the time \NI started thinking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.86,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that he was killed by \Nanother member of his own squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.54,0:17:37.92,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No way! He must've been \None hell of an annoyance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.65,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,if there are rumors like that going around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.74,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He probably showed off too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:46.79,flashback,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter. \NThis just means another peasant died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.05,flashbackitalics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.73,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just happening \Nwith the Magic Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:18:00.18,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom, because of \Nthe class they were born into,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.06,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,the ones on top grew arrogant while \Nthe ones at the bottom gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.06,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Even though both sides \Nshould've had more potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.57,0:18:09.56,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:12.81,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The potential of magic \Nand of humans is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.32,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,For your voice to be widely \Nheard, you need power,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.82,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,rank,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.57,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:24.33,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I built up a record of achievements \Nand became the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:29.58,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Magic and humans should be freer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.63,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The change won't be dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.26,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,However, slowly but surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:39.59,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,The people of this kingdom are \Nfinally starting to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:44.56,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Through the strength of the people \NI believe in and acknowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:47.52,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Through the strength of the \Npeople they acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:51.10,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that end now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:54.61,italics,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Not while I am the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.11,main,Julius,0000,0000,0000,,Time Reversal Magic: Chrono Anastasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.79,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.62,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,A time spell tremendous enough to save \Nall the people of this kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.58,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.05,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But it appears that you've \Nused up all the time and magic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.58,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,that you had accumulated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.33,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you saw my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.34,0:19:59.42,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,But you couldn't cancel that time spell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:01.38,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,in order to evade.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.51,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.76,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,you are the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.15,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you are the Wizard King...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:26.65,main,Licht,0000,0000,0000,,That is your one and only weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's going on here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:20:58.18,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:35.50,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.90,0:22:34.30,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:39.00,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Please, Calm Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.66,0:22:37.23,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Calm Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:40.98,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.56,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is Lord Julius fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:45.46,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:46.97,main,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Please, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.22,0:22:50.11,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:53.43,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job to remain \Ncalm at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.77,0:22:56.27,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Lord Julius should lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:59.47,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,but if all else fails, the only ones \Nwho could keep up in this battle are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:01.53,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Knights Squad captains or their equals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:04.15,italics,Marx,0000,0000,0000,,I need to send a message to all the \NMagic Knights Squad headquarters I've marked!
